  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Strengthening Civil Registration and Vital Statistics (CRVS) in Sierra Leone to Ensure Legal Identity for All</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project is designed as a joint UN project. The UN project team will engage other UN agencies through the UN Task Force to advance essential event registration and other related initiatives to facilitate access to financial services, following agency mandates outlined in the UNCT Operational Guidelines. IOM role will focus on updating standard operation procedure for linking registration and legal identity confirmation for refugee, migrant, displaced and stateless populations.</narrative>
  </description>
